2.Events
2.1 Mouse Events

events: 
click
dblclick
mouseover

write button class in html:<button>Button</button>
write funtion in js: let btn = $('button'); btn.on('click dblclick mouseover',function(){console.log('Have a nice day!'); })

2.2 Keyboard Events

events:
keypress
keydown
keyup

2.3 Form Events
submit
change
focus

2.4 Window Events
load
resize
scroll

